    "Research QuestionsThe research questions addressed by this study are: With respect to the research question concerning the amount (RQ1) of the research, the mapping study addresses this.",
    "We limited the search to the period 2009-2021.",
    "We recognize that the number of review papers prior to 2009 was scarce.",
    "However, there were relevant studies also prior to 2009, and we looked in few of them to have an idea of the prior research [7,8].",
    "To answer the RQ1, we identified the number of papers on smart building energy and the journals that published them."
